			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				After reading several of these posts I realize that most of you have most likely never been into that cave, I have ventured into many, many times before. The wandering guy &quot;spellcaster&quot; is a necro in his mid to high 40's and his name is the Lich of Miragul, he does have a pet, and he is VERY aggro. Also! Sulon Mcmoor is near lvl 60, so ummm....stay away from him. He hit me for 400+ dmg one time and  I ran my little butt outa there till I got my bearings back = P. There was a goblin in the room not too far away from him but I couldn't get to him cuz of Sulon, everything in there is very very very hard to kill for there lvls and the place is rather LARGE, so good luck finding the bear that I never saw!<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
Some guy
